txt.en: 'I think the young gentlehobbits of Bree are much more sophisticated than the provincial hobbits of Staddle.'
'I want to go live in Bree, but my father won't let me.'
'Would you pass the jam? We never seem to have enough! We're not out are we?'
'Oh, how I long for adventure! You don't think me queer do you? Everyone around here does.'
